room_title: Escape room "Road Trip '66" by The Fantastic Escape! in Cedar Rapids
room_description:
It is 1966 and you have been undercover for months now. The assignment is to drive your Chevrolet across the USA in hot pursuit of counterfeiters who are filling the small towns of America with fake $50's.
It has been a long trip in a car with a faulty heater, no air conditioning and barely a radio. But now, with evidence in hand, you will be reporting back to the FBI in the morning. Just one last stop to make...
